                                                  167 of 2021</ref>)</sourceNote></content></paragraph></subsection></section><section id="ID_1438402958615_003" name="s4" reason="repealed" startPeriod="1998-07-10" status="repealed" temporalId="s4"><num value="4">4.</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="/hk/1998/ln116">L.N. 116 of 1998</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438402958631_002" name="s5" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2022-05-31" status="operational" temporalId="s5"><num value="5">5.</num><heading>Disapplication</heading><subsection id="ID_1639471068859_001" name="1" temporalId="s5_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><leadIn>This Order shall not apply to—
                <sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2021/ln167">L.N. 167 of
                2021</ref>)</sourceNote></leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438411838865_012" name="a" temporalId="s5_1_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>any building erected in accordance with plans approved by the Building
                    Authority before
                    31
                    May 2022;</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411838865_020" name="b" temporalId="s5_1_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>any building that, at the time of erection, was exempted from the
                    provisions of the Buildings Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap123">Cap. 123</ref>) by
                    virtue of <ref>section 41(1)(a)</ref> of that Ordinance;</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411838865_028" name="c" temporalId="s5_1_c"><num value="c">(c)</num><content>any building that, at the time of erection, was exempted from the
                    provisions of the Buildings Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap123">Cap. 123</ref>) by
                    virtue of <ref>section 41(1)(aa)</ref> of that Ordinance and is erected by or on
                    behalf of the Housing Authority in accordance with plans endorsed by the Housing
                    Authority
                    or
                    the Office of the Permanent Secretary for Transport and Housing (Housing) before
                    31 May 2022;</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411838881_006" name="d" temporalId="s5_1_d"><num value="d">(d)</num><content>any building erected before
                    31
                    May 2022 that, at the time of erection, was exempted from the
                    provisions of the Buildings Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap123">Cap. 123</ref>) by
                    virtue of <ref>section 41(1)(b)</ref> of that
                    Ordinance;</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1639471068864_002" name="e" temporalId="s5_1_e"><num value="e">(e)</num><leadIn>part of a building referred to in paragraph (a) or (c) that comprises a
                    structure the construction of which is minor works or designated exempted
                    works—</leadIn><subparagraph id="ID_1639471068865_003" name="1" temporalId="s5_1_e_1"><num value="1">(i)</num><content>carried out in relation to the external part of the building;
                        and</content></subparagraph><subparagraph id="ID_1639471068865_004" name="2" temporalId="s5_1_e_2"><num value="2">(ii)</num><content>completed before 31 May 2022; and <sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2021/ln167">L.N. 167 of 2021</ref>)</sourceNote></content></subparagraph></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1639471068867_005" name="f" temporalId="s5_1_f"><num value="f">(f)</num><content>any building that is a structure projecting skywards the construction of
                    which is minor works or designated exempted works completed before 31 May 2022.
                            <sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2021/ln167">L.N. 167 of
                        2021</ref>)</sourceNote></content></paragraph></subsection><subsection id="ID_1639471068869_006" name="2" temporalId="s5_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><leadIn>In this section—</leadIn><def name="BuildingAuthority"><term>Building Authority</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">建築事務監督</term>) means the Director of Buildings;</def><def name="DesignatedExemptedWorks"><term>designated exempted works</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">指定豁免工程</term>) has the meaning given by <ref>section
                    2(1)</ref> of the Building (Minor Works) Regulation (<ref href="/hk/cap123N">Cap. 123 sub. leg. N</ref>);</def><def name="MinorWorks"><term>minor works</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">小型工程</term>) has the meaning given by <ref>section 2(1)</ref> of the Buildings
                Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap123">Cap. 123</ref>);</def><def name="PlansApprovedByTheBuildingAuthority">
                <leadIn><term>plans approved by the Building Authority</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">建築事務監督批准的圖則</term>) means plans approved by the
                    Building Authority under—</leadIn>
                <paragraph id="ID_1639471068871_007" name="a" temporalId="s5_2_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>the Buildings Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap123">Cap. 123</ref>);
                        or</content></paragraph>
                <paragraph id="ID_1639471068872_008" name="b" temporalId="s5_2_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>the Buildings Ordinance 1935 (<ref href="/hk/1935/18">18 of
                        1935</ref>). <sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2021/ln167">L.N. 167 of
                            2021</ref>)</sourceNote></content></paragraph>
            </def></subsection><sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2021/ln167">L.N. 167 of 2021</ref>)</sourceNote></section></main></subLeg>